node.text:
Our hearts couldn’t be more full finally being able to do what we love again. The vibes are: ❤️‍🔥😍✨👌🏻🥲🎉🔥

Who’s excited to see our stunt?! 👀💓

Check the tags to follow this year’s flyers. They’re incredible. ✨

node.text:
New gdub alert 🚨 🥰 🦈 

Our coach @alimoffatt welcomed the most precious, beautiful, baby girl into the world. We can’t wait to meet Willa and give her never ending love.

Ali, you’re already the very best coach, but you’re going to be an even better mom. We all love you so much.

node.text: HAPPY BIRTHDAY to @emilyvesterfelt 🥰 you are this team’s ultimate hype girl and we wouldn’t have it any other way. You’re a forever OG that means SO much to every single one of us. We hope you had the best day and we can’t wait to see you at practice xo! ✨♥️

node.text: HAPPY BIRTHDAY to our brightest light @_lauren._.elizabeth ✨You’ve always been the most supportive teammate, sister, and best friend to every gdub. You’re talented beyond measure, but more importantly, you create joy everywhere you go. Thanks for being you. Have the best day Stanley!

node.text: HAPPY BIRTHDAY to our legendary power shark 🦈 @jennpower0303 ✨ Thank you for being such an encouraging and supportive leader to this team. You’re an incredible coach and you have nothing but respect and love from us all. You’re an actual super hero 🦸🏼‍♀️ - Hope your day is almost as special as you. xo

node.text: We can’t wait to introduce you to the 2021-2022 Gdubs. We’re back. 😏

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Cheer Sport Great White Sharks on June 13, 2021 tagging @ameliaa.mae. May be an image of 1 person, standing and text that says '2019 H 2019 WORLD INTERNATIONAL OPEN CHAMPION GOLD CHAMPION LEVEL 5 2019 YKORE Lin'.

node.text: Happy belated birthday to this ray of sunshine ☀️💓 We absolutely adore you - from an incredible flyer to a fantastic teammate, you bring so much heart and positivity to our team. You are so special to all of us. We love you so much! Xo

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Cheer Sport Great White Sharks on June 05, 2021 tagging @kianahorchover. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Happy Birthday Horch! 💖 We are so lucky to have someone as special as you in our lives. You shine so bright both on and off the cheer floor and bring so much love to this team. We love you! ✨ @kianahorchover

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Cheer Sport Great White Sharks on May 28, 2021 tagging @chelseamatteson, and @paytoooon. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and text that says 'Creat Whites Great Whites'.

node.text:
Here’s what @paytoooon aka Diddy had to say about her experience being on this magical team. 🥰

If you want the chance at being a part of the most special group of people, you can send a tryout video to info@cheersportsharks.com 
Make sure to include your ~highest level~ of stunting and tumbling skills.

Limited spots are available. Take the first step towards making your biggest dream come true. ⭐️
